{"tid":1526293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點做先可以俾被拘捕者先送院治理","createTime":"2019-09-01T05:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:24:14.000Z","uid":182620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2414997ee4cd64f097b3b05177d29912a6ecd968","tid":1526293,"uid":182620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:16:03.000Z","msg":"其實有冇辦法申請人道救援或入稟法院要求先將傷者送醫治療先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvupgT2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvupgT2.png&h=c5583dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0D3A70J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0D3A70J.png&h=96f3a622&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63eef152bef87d813c81531b81369d1e5f762e9a","tid":1526293,"uid":177336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:16:52.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X6nyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=a2c83425\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F